<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 12:21:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>律师称在澳大利亚被捕的美国海军陆战队飞行员与中国黑客合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-marine-pilot-arrested-australia-worked-with-chinese-hacker-lawyer-says-2024-05-12/</link><description>一名前美国海军陆战队飞行员因美国指控训练中国军事飞行员在航母上着陆而反对从澳大利亚引渡，他的律师表示，他在不知情的情况下与一名中国黑客合作。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 10:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-marine-pilot-arrested-australia-worked-with-chinese-hacker-lawyer-says-2024-05-12/</guid></item><item><title>英国登山家记录了外国人攀登珠穆朗玛峰最多的纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-mountaineer-logs-most-everest-climbs-by-foreigner-nepali-makes-29th-ascent-2024-05-12/</link><description>徒步旅行官员周日表示，一名英国登山者和一名尼泊尔向导打破了他们自己保持的世界最高峰珠穆朗玛峰攀登次数记录。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 06:58:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-mountaineer-logs-most-everest-climbs-by-foreigner-nepali-makes-29th-ascent-2024-05-12/</guid></item><item><title>半岛电视台称，印度尼西亚总理普拉博沃重申以“亚洲方式”化解紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-reiterates-asian-way-defuse-tension-al-jazeera-says-2024-05-12/</link><description>随着印度尼西亚当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 准备于 10 月份就职，他似乎将在外交政策上采取更加自信的立场，称外交、谈判和“亚洲方式”有助于化解紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 06:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-reiterates-asian-way-defuse-tension-al-jazeera-says-2024-05-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国工商银行将启动 TLAC 债券发行，发行 41.5 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-icbc-kick-off-tlac-bond-sales-with-issuance-415-bln-2024-05-12/</link><description>中国工商银行表示，将于 5 月 15 日发行 300 亿元人民币（41.5 亿美元）的总损失吸收能力（TLAC）债券，这是中资银行首次发行此类债券。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 03:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-icbc-kick-off-tlac-bond-sales-with-issuance-415-bln-2024-05-12/</guid></item><item><title>科威尔在亚冠夺冠后保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kewell-guards-against-complacency-after-asian-champions-league-win-2024-05-11/</link><description>尽管在周六的亚洲冠军联赛决赛中，他率领横滨水手队在主场以 2-1 领先，但主教练哈里·科威尔仍然对埃尔南·克雷斯波的艾因队构成的威胁保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 22:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kewell-guards-against-complacency-after-asian-champions-league-win-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>另有八个中国城市加入香港独自旅游计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eight-more-chinese-cities-join-hong-kong-solo-travel-scheme-2024-05-11/</link><description>又有八个中国城市加入了一项计划，允许居民自行前往香港，而不是跟团，作为促进香港经济的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 13:22:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eight-more-chinese-cities-join-hong-kong-solo-travel-scheme-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾派遣船只前往中国建造“人工岛”的争议环礁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-ships-disputed-atoll-where-china-building-artificial-island-2024-05-11/</link><description>菲律宾周六表示，已向南海争议地区部署船只，并指责中国在不断升级的海上争端中建造“人工岛”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 11:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-ships-disputed-atoll-where-china-building-artificial-island-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国碧桂园在宽限期内偿还境内优惠券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-repays-onshore-coupons-within-grace-period-2024-05-11/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商碧桂园在周六的一份声明中表示，继上周未能付款后，该公司已在五天宽限期到期前偿还了两笔境内债券票息。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:46:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-repays-onshore-coupons-within-grace-period-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国公司赢得伊拉克油气田勘探许可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/iraq-launches-oil-gas-licensing-round-29-projects-2024-05-11/</link><description>周六，中国公司在一轮碳氢化合物勘探许可中赢得了勘探伊拉克五个油气田的投标，该轮勘探主要旨在提高国内天然气产量。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 08:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/iraq-launches-oil-gas-licensing-round-29-projects-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国居民消费价格连续第三个月上涨 预示需求复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-3rd-month-factory-deflation-persists-2024-05-11/</link><description>4月份，中国消费者价格连续第三个月上涨，而生产者价格则延续跌势，这表明在北京应对提振经济的挑战之际，内需有所改善。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 01:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-3rd-month-factory-deflation-persists-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，在美国上市面临障碍的情况下，Shein 加强了伦敦 IPO 的准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，快时尚巨头 Shein 正在加紧准备在伦敦上市，此前该公司试图在纽约上市，但面临监管障碍和美国立法者的阻力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国市场首次亮相，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国汽车出口创历史新高，但国内销量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五的数据显示，由于价格竞争加剧以及消费者在经济复苏不稳定的情况下对大件消费持谨慎态度，国内销量同比下滑 5.8%，中国 4 月份汽车出口飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示坚决反对美国出口管制工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</link><description>在美国出于国家安全考虑将37家中国企业列入贸易限制名单后，外交部发言人周五表示，中国坚决反对滥用美国实体清单等出口管制工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>